01:28:18,092 --> 01:28:20,788
Mother just can't tell you
anymore tonight.

1559
01:28:20,928 --> 01:28:23,556
Oh, Mommy, please.

1560
01:28:25,933 --> 01:28:27,924
What is the matter, Mommy?

1561
