The New Year's Party.

1602
01:31:08,796 --> 01:31:12,630
But, of course
you don't feel like going.

1603
01:31:12,767 --> 01:31:15,201
Pierre, we promised.

1604
01:31:15,336 --> 01:31:21,172
Let's go.
I'd rather. Might help.

